events.name: FoodImportRequested
events.description: Captures the initiation of a food import request by a client.

events.name: FoodImportConfirmed
events.description: Indicates that the food import request has been confirmed by the supplier.

events.name: FoodImportShipped
events.description: Denotes that the food items have been shipped from the supplier.

events.name: FoodImportReceived
events.description: Marks the event of food items being received at the warehouse.

commands.name: RequestFoodImport
commands.description: Captures the initiation of a food import request by a client.

commands.name: ConfirmFoodImport
commands.description: Indicates that the food import request has been confirmed by the supplier.

commands.name: ShipFoodImport
commands.description: Denotes that the food items have been shipped from the supplier.

commands.name: ReceiveFoodImport
commands.description: Marks the event of food items being received at the warehouse.

integrationPoints.name: SupplierManagement
integrationPoints.description: Integration with the Supplier Management system for tracking supplier details and food import requests.

integrationPoints.name: WarehouseManagement
integrationPoints.description: Integrates with the Warehouse Management system to update stock levels upon receiving food imports.

integrationPoints.name: OrderProcessing
integrationPoints.description: Connection to Order Processing for handling customer orders related to food imports.
